<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Thank You | Brownson Industrial Consulting</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;}
    body{
      min-height:100vh;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(9,27,56,.88), rgba(9,27,56,.92)),
        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092580497-e0d23cbdf1dc?q=80&w=1800&auto=format&fit=crop');
      background-size:cover;
      background-position:center;
      color:#fff;
      padding:24px;
    }
    .card{
      max-width:760px;
      width:100%;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.10);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
      backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
      border-radius:28px;
      padding:48px 34px;
      text-align:center;
      box-shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
    }
    .badge{
      width:80px;height:80px;border-radius:24px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f57c00,#ff9f43);
      display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
      margin:0 auto 22px;font-size:34px;font-weight:900;
      box-shadow:0 14px 34px rgba(245,124,0,.30);
    }
    h1{font-size:44px;line-height:1.08;margin-bottom:16px;}
    p{font-size:18px;line-height:1.9;color:#eef4ff;max-width:620px;margin:0 auto 26px;}
    .btn{
      display:inline-block;padding:16px 28px;border-radius:14px;background:#f57c00;color:#fff;
      text-decoration:none;font-weight:800;box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(245,124,0,.25);
    }
    .btn:hover{opacity:.95;}
    .sub{
      margin-top:24px;font-size:14px;color:#d7e3f7;
    }
    @media (max-width:700px){
      h1{font-size:34px;}
      p{font-size:17px;}
      .card{padding:36px 24px;}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="badge">✓</div>
    <h1>Thank You for Reaching Out</h1>
    <p>
      Your consultation request has been submitted successfully.
      Brownson Industrial Consulting will review your message and follow up as soon as possible.
    </p>
    <a href="index.html" class="btn">Back to Website</a>
    <div class="sub">
      Brownson Industrial Consulting • Industrial Maintenance • Reliability Support • Downtime Reduction
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
